Nisa kemudian mencuba nasib dan memberitahu Reza yang dia ingin menjalin hubungan yang lebih serius dengan Reza. Dan ini bermakna Reza berkemungkinan besar perlu menceraikan isterinya.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep03
programme.desc: Ibu shira dapat rasakan Shira dilamun cinta kerana sanggup cuba makan budu. Cuti pertengahan semester bermula dan Faizul balik ke Kelantan. programme.desc: Nenda Delisha sejak awal pagi menasihati anak menantunya yang langsung tak bimbang tentang Delisha. Dalam pada itu, Zainal mendapati sikap Salima berbeza. programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep07
programme.desc: Airil membuat kejutan membawa sejambak bunga di resort tempat Fatihah bekerja. Lebih memeranjatkan ketika itu Nizam ada bersama Fatihah. Aleya juga begitu teruja melihat kehadiran ayahnya. Pada mulanya hanya Aleya dan Airil meluangkan masa bersama tetapi setelah beberapa kali memujuk Fatihah, akhirnya Fatihah bersetuju mengambil cuti demi Airil dan Aleya. Malangnya, Nizam yang mula cemburu sengaja membuat Fatihah agar tiada masa bersama Airil. Airil yang mengetahui niat Nizam memberinya amaran agar jangan mengganggu Fatihah. Fatihah kecewa melihat kejadian itu menuduh Airil cemburu buta dengan mana-mana lelaki yang cuba mendekatinya. Dia berhak untuk teruskan hidup kalau Airil masih tidak berubah. Ia semakin mencabar Airil. Norlin akhirnya setuju menemukan Arif dengan keluarganya tetapi memberi amaran pada Normah supaya menjaga mulutnya. Sebelum pulang ke kampung, lagi sekali Airil memberi amaran kepada Nizam.

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep04
programme.desc: Tangan Faizul retak dan ditahan di wad akibat kemalangan. Dari luar wad, Shira terdengar Faizul sedang video call dengan seseorang. Shira gelisah dan tanya Arman. Katanya, itu Sha, mungkin kekasih Faizul. Semester depan, Sha akan balik semula ke kampus. Selepas dua hari di wad, Arman hantar Faizul balik ke Kelantan yang dapat cuti sakit. Di KL, Shira nyatakan hasratnya mahu meminang Faizul. Datuk Badrul menentang tetapi akhirnya setuju. Faizul dan Mek Yan terkejut dengan kehadiran Shira sekeluarga. Faizul yang tahu bisnes berjaya tambat hati Datuk Badrul sehingga beliau setuju meminang Faizul. Mek Yan marah Faizul, perempuan di situ tak ada yang meminang lelaki. Namun, akhirnya Mek Yan restu hubungan itu tetapi biar mereka yang datang meminang Shira. Pertunangan pun berlangsung

programme.desc: Delisha semakin menyukai Faiq dan mereka sering keluar hingga lewat malam. Tingkahlaku itu membuatkan nendanya terus bimbang, nendanya berbincang dengan ibu bapa Delisha serta Ustaz Ghazali untuk menjodohkan Delisha dengan Ustaz Ghazali. Delisha membantah. Sultan mempercayai pemilik selipar itu yang pernah menyelamatkan istana dari api yang marak. Setelah pencarian, Pak Kodi yang dikesan sebagai tuan punya selipar dan bakal berkahwin dengan puterinya. programme.desc: Sementara Feka dan Shah berada di Perth, Nenek Shah dan Husna tidak dapat menghubungi Shah atau Feka. Dalam pada itu, Husna datang dengan tiba-tiba. Feka berbual dengan Damia dan memaklumkan dia akan balik ke rumah ibu bapanya setelah dapat izin Shah. Shah yang tiba di rumah ibu bapanya, akui dia silap dan meminta masa untuk dia betulkan kesilapannya. Dia juga berjanji Feka tetap tidak akan diceraikan. Husna bermati matian ingin berehat di rumah Shah, sedangkan Shah tidak mahu dia tinggal di rumah Shah. Keesokan pagi Husna siapkan minum pagi. Shah kehairanan apa yang berlaku semalam selepas dia tertidur kerana rasanya Husna balik ke rumahnya.

programme.title: Halalkan Hati Yang Ku Curi S1 Ep26
programme.desc: Delisha selamat melahirkan anak di sebuah hospital swasta. Bagi Gayah, dia terpaksa membawa Delisha ke situ kerana dia tahu pasangan itu tidak mampu. Di samping itu, Gayah dan Sabar mendesak memberikan anak mereka sebagai jaminan. Pun begitu, Faiq terpaksa menanda surat janji dengan Gayah. Apabila Faiq bersama isteri dan bayi mereka balik ke rumah, Gayah dan Sabar mendesak Faiq. Delisha terus merayu kepada Gayah, Gayah terus membawa keluar bayi mereka. Dengan usaha Abang Ali, dia dapat menahan semula Gayah dan Sabar, bayi diambil semula kerana resit bayaran ada dengan Abang Ali. Abang Ali menyerahkan bayi itu kepada isteri imam (haji), Kak Anum. Dia kemudiannya membawa bayi itu ke pangkuan Delisha dan Faiq. Sebelum itu melalui Abang Ali, Faiq telah diperkenalkan kepada Datuk Sofia, Faiq ditemuduga dan akhirnya diterima sebagai eksekutif disyarikatnya. Syarikat datuk berkaitan dengan perniagaan reka bentuk dan fesyen. Faiq kemudiannya juga membawa Delisha untuk diperkenalkan kepada datuk kerana Delisha berkemahiran di bidang itu .Suatu hari di pertengahan Delisha sedang asyik menerangkan sesuatu, tiba-tiba Nenda, Datuk Rosnah, ibu dan bapa Faiq dan ibu bapa Delisha dituruti Ustaz Ghazali.

programme.title: Cicakman 2
programme.desc: Profesor Klon yang jahat kembali, bukan sahaja untuk menggulingkan Kerajaan tetapi juga untuk mengawal bekalan air tawar dunia melalui rancangannya yang bijak, "Air Hitam". Apabila planet biru kita hanya mempunyai 72 jam sebelum menjadi hitam, Cicakman datang untuk menyelamatkan. Tetapi dia bukan sahaja berhadapan dengan pembunuh upahan artistik Profesor Klon "Rrama", tetapi juga musuh lamanya, Ginger Boys, yang telah kembali dalam bentuk rohani yang kuat.

programme.title: Two Cops Ep16

programme.title: Hunter Killer
programme.desc: Kapal selam kelas Los Angeles AS USS Tampa Bay hilang ketika membayangi kapal selam kelas Akula Rusia Konek di Artik. Laksamana Muda John Fisk (Common) menghantar kapal selam kelas Virginia USS Arkansas, di bawah perintah Komander Joe Glass (Gerard Butler) yang baru dinaikkan pangkat dan tidak ortodoks untuk menyiasat. Pada masa yang sama, pasukan Navy SEAL di bawah pimpinan Leftenan Bill Beaman dihantar untuk memerhatikan pangkalan tentera laut Rusia secara diam-diam. Apabila mereka tiba di pangkalan tentera laut, mereka menyaksikan menteri pertahanan Dmitri Durov melakukan rampasan kuasa dan menawan Presiden Rusia Zakarin, dan dengan cepat menyedari bahawa Durov berhasrat untuk mencetuskan perang.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep6
programme.desc: Akil pulang kerumah dari bengkel dan dapati saka Mayang Kasturi sedang menunggunya. Mayang Kasturi minta tolong Akil mencari rantai miliknya yang sekarang ini dalam milik seorang perempuan yang berambut panjang dan suka memakai baju kebaya. Mayang Kasturi mahu rantai itu untuk membolehnya pulang ke habitat asalnya dan berjanji tidak akan mengganggu Akil atau manusia lain lagi. Akil ingin tahu cerita rantai itu. Mayang Kasturi mengguna kuasa sakanya menidurkan Akil dan dalam tidur dia terlihat Mayang Kasturi berkawan dengan seorang gadis bernama Ally. Sejak berkawan dengan Mayang Kasturi, Ally berubah sikap dan suka melawan dan tidak mendengar cakap ibunya lagi. Bomoh Tok Misai berjaya menghalau Mayang Kasturi daripada Ally dan telah mengambil rantai saka milik Mayang Kasturi. Mayang Kasturi mahu semula rantai itu. Akil berjanji akan membantu dan secara kebetulan dia terlihat Siti, kerani di bengkelnya memakai rantai tersebut. Akil membuat tawaran untuk membeli rantai itu daripada Siti tetapi gagal. Akhirnya Akil berjaya memiliki rantai itu apabila Siti tertinggal di bilik mandi. Rantai itu diserah kepada Mayang Kasturi yang berjanji tidak akan mengganggu Akil lagi.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep2
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Plan B Ep1
programme.desc: Episod pertama ini mengisahkan Khai dan Airis kedua-dua mereka daripada keluarga kaya mempertaruhkan wang dalam satu perlumbaan haram kereta "drift". Airis memenangi perlumbaan itu dengan imbuhan wang sebanyak RM20 ribu. Khai tidak berpuas hati, kerana Airis yang dikatakan baru dalam aktiviti ini dengan mudah mengalahkannya. Khai meneruskan usahanya untuk berkenalan dengan Airis dengan bantuan rakanya, Que mendapatkan butir peribadi, Airis menerusi laman sosial "FB".

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Episod ke 12 ini memaparkan antara lain Adrus masih berkeadaan tidak normal. Kali ini kelakuan agresifnya hingga menyebabkan badannya bertukar bentuk dan warna kulitnya hijau seperti 'Hulk'. Sambil itu dia mengancam ahli keluarganya, tetapi dengan keberanian Nia berdepan, di samping memohon perkara yang tidak baik dihindarkan, tiba-tiba Adrus berubah kepada asal, tetapi masih tidak sedar diri. Ibrahim, isterinya dan Pak Abas terus membincangkan tentang Gelam yang bersifat meresapi dalam jiwa manusia. Lantaran itu manusia berkenaan akan gelisah. Situasi itulah dialami Zeti, malahan dia juga bercakap dalam dua nada. Sementara itu Datin Salina selain dalam ketakutan kerana terserempak dengan lembaga putih, dia mula bercakap berseorangan. Lebih parah, pejabatnya menerima notis untuk di sita. Nia telah menemui Fauzan setelah dia diminta membantu. Sebelum itu, Adrus telah kembali normal dan pulih. Dia bersama bapanya mengekori Nia bimbangkan sesuatu terjadi.

programme.title: Vikingdom
programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah masa datang dentingan keluli terhadap keluli, pertembungan mitos, sejarah dan fiksyen…. "Vikingdom". Secara longgar berdasarkan legenda Viking dan puisi epik yang mereka tinggalkan sebagai rekod, dengan tafsiran kreatif, "Vikingdom" ialah fantasi, pengembaraan aksi tentang raja yang dilupakan, Eirick, yang ditugaskan dengan kemungkinan mustahil untuk mengalahkan Thor, Dewa Petir.

programme.title: Hantu Gendong Susu
programme.desc: Darma mengajak kekasihnya Virna dan kawannya Mulan dan Andre ke kampungnya. Kedatangan mereka tidak diterima oleh ayah Darma.Darma kenal dengan seorang gadis di situ. Darma mendapati dia sudah kenal dengan Prapti di dalam mimpinya. Darma mendapati ayahnya sering mengadakan ritual pada waktu malam. Darma dan kawannya terancam.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep5
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Maira yang sebelum ini takut dan enggan berkawan dengan Imran, Haikal dan Zara kerana mereka memiliki kuasa magik akhirnya kembali berbaik semula setelah menyedari dia juga memiliki kuasa magik yang boleh membekukan air.Turut dipaparkan kisah Hariman yang baru bebas dari penjara datang bertemu Salim di kedainya untuk mengetahui tentang batu permata yang mereka curi lima tahun lalu. Haikal yang berulang alik ke kedai Salim untuk membeli dan menukar layang-layang sempat bertanya tentang identiti Hariman namun Salim yang cuba menyembunyikan perkara sebenar telah membuat pengakuan bahawa Hariman adalah sepupunya.

programme.title: Hikayat Merong Mahawangsa
programme.desc: Pada tahun 120, Empayar Rom ketika itu di bawah pemerintahan Hadrian sementara di negara China, Dinasti Han merupakan sebuah empayar yang kuat dan telah memperluaskan pemerintahannya ke negara Asia Tengah. Semasa angkatan Rom sedang membaik pulih kapal mereka di Goa, mereka meminta pertolongan Merong Mahawangsa mengiringi Putera Rom ke Langkasuka (dikatakan terletak di utara Malaysia) untuk berkahwin dengan seorang Puteri China yang cantik dari Dinasti Han.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Halim bersama Maya berada di hospital melawat Echa bertemu Arifah yang datang menziarahi Mat. Mat yang patah kaki kirinya menceritakan apa yang terjadi pada dirinya sendiri. Mat sempat membisikkan pada Halim supaya berhati-hati dengan Husin. Nina dirumah dirasuk. Halim yang dalam perjalanan pulang, berselisihan dengan Nina berjalan seorang diri "sleepwalking". Halim membawa Nina pulang. Tetapi sebaik sahaja Halim masuk ke dalam rumah, dia terperanjat melihat Nina sedang dirawati Dukun Induk. Husin ada bersama dalam rumah Halim. Halim meluru keluar melihat Nina yang dibawa pulang tadi, rupanya hanyalah batang pokok pisang ditempat duduk penumpang.

programme.title: Terowong Ep6
programme.desc: Episod 6, bertajuk ' Surat' ini mengisahkan Ramli yang ingin memiliki harta bapa mentuanya telah membuat perjanjian dalam sekeping surat dengan seorang tua yang dijumpainya di dalam terowong semasa dia berjoging. Setelah dia berjaya,Ramli telah dihantui dengan tuntutan janji orang tua tersebut supaya Ramli membawa darah manusia untuk semahan di dalam terowong itu. Dalam pada itu dengan pertolongan bekas kekasihnya, isteri Ramli telah meminta pertolongan seorang bomoh (orang tua) yang sama untuk mengatasi masalah Ramli yang suka bermain kayu tiga. Malangnya dengan hasutan bomoh tersebut Ramli yang cemburu terhadap isterinya dengan rakan sepejabatnya itu telah membunuh mereka berdua. Bomoh itu juga telah berpesan kepada Ramli supaya membawa korban kepadanya dan dua tahun kemudian, Ramli membawa kekasihnya pula untuk dikorbankan tetapi kali ini Ramli sendiri turut menjadi korban bomoh tersebut

programme.desc: Darma mengajak kekasihnya Virna dan kawannya Mulan dan Andre ke kampungnya. Kedatangan mereka tidak diterima oleh ayah Darma.Darma kenal dengan seorang gadis di situ. Darma mendapati dia sudah kenal dengan Prapti di dalam mimpinya. Darma mendapati ayahnya sering mengadakan ritual pada waktu malam. Darma dan kawannya terancam.

Semasa angkatan Rom sedang membaik pulih kapal mereka di Goa, mereka meminta pertolongan Merong Mahawangsa mengiringi Putera Rom ke Langkasuka (dikatakan terletak di utara Malaysia) untuk berkahwin dengan seorang Puteri China yang cantik dari Dinasti Han.

programme.desc: Edwin dan Netta bersama dua anak mereka, Agam dan Sekar, kembali ke kampung Netta di Temanggung. programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.title: Hunter Killer
programme.desc: Kapal selam kelas Los Angeles AS USS Tampa Bay hilang ketika membayangi kapal selam kelas Akula Rusia Konek di Artik. Laksamana Muda John Fisk (Common) menghantar kapal selam kelas Virginia USS Arkansas, di bawah perintah Komander Joe Glass (Gerard Butler) yang baru dinaikkan pangkat dan tidak ortodoks untuk menyiasat. Pada masa yang sama, pasukan Navy SEAL di bawah pimpinan Leftenan Bill Beaman dihantar untuk memerhatikan pangkalan tentera laut Rusia secara diam-diam. Apabila mereka tiba di pangkalan tentera laut, mereka menyaksikan menteri pertahanan Dmitri Durov melakukan rampasan kuasa dan menawan Presiden Rusia Zakarin, dan dengan cepat menyedari bahawa Durov berhasrat untuk mencetuskan perang.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Episod terakhir yang mengisahkan Pak Bado dijumpai mati dibunuh. Disebabkan ini, Ramdi telah memberitahu Ustaz Hambali apa yang berlaku kepada Sarakit yang dirogol dan kemudiannya dibunuh Pak Bado. Ustaz Hambali telah berusaha menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi dengan memulihkan semangat Rafiq dan menghalau jin Sarakit dari badan Dina. Akibatnya Dina telah meninggal dunia. Dengan bantuan orang-orang kampung, mereka berjaya berjumpa kubur Sarakit dan Rafiq redha dengan apa yang berlaku terhadap Sarakit. Rafiq meninggalkan kampung dan Ramdi kemudiannya menjadi buta apabila terjatuh mencederakan matanya.

programme.title: Chikaro
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Gemerlapan
programme.desc: Mimi mengejutkan ramai pelajar di sebuah kolej berprestij kerana menjadi seorang penggemar muzik dangdut yang tegar. Nel, salah seorang pelajar di situ menganggap muzik dangdut kekampungan dan mereka berdua sering bertengkar kerana hal tersebut. Tetapi tanpa disedari, Nel adalah Mr X yang selama ini merupakan peminat rahsia Mimi dalam diam.

programme.title: Putera
programme.desc: Seorang putera raja bernama Hussein menemui cinta bersama seorang gadis biasa. Namun dia dijodohkan bersama Puteri Balqis. Mereka ke Paris namun Hussein terlihat Balqis bermesraan bersama lelaki lain. Bapa Hussein memeberinya masa selama 30 hari untuk mencari calon isteri jika tidak mahu berkahwin dengan Puteri Balqis. Pelbagai halangan terpaksa mereka tempuhi demi mengecapi cinta.

programme.title: Amelia
programme.desc: Amelia menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fandy setelah mereka bertemu secara tidak sengaja di Cameron Highlands. Dalam masa yang sama ibu Amelia ingin menjodohkannya dengan Jefri. Amelia enggan menurut kehendak ibunya kerana Jefri seorang kaki perempuan. Bapa Amelia juga menentang keputusan itu dan bertemu Fandy untuk menceritakan segala yang berlaku. Fandy berasa bersalah kerana menganggap dirinya punca keluarga Amelia berantakan. Fandy mengambil keputusan untuk membawa diri ke luar negara dan hal ini telah menyebabkan Amelia terpaksa mengahwini Jefri. Selepas berkahwin, Amelia dijangkiti HIV daripada suaminya. Apabila Fandy mengetahui keadaan sebenar, dia ingin menebus segala kesalahannya terhadap Amelia.

programme.title: Hanny
programme.desc: Cinta Hanny dan Jeff dihalang oleh ayahnya, Dato’ Mansor. Hanny pulang ke kampung bapanya dan ditunangkan dengan Faizal. Jeff memberontak dan hidup sendiri dengan mengambil upah membawa teksi setelah keluar daripada rumahnya apabila Dato’ Mansor ingin menjodohkannya dengan Maria.Sofea yang juga kakak kepada Jeff telah mengupah seorang wanita bernama Sheila untuk mengintip perhubungan Jeff dan Hanny dan merosakkan hubungan mereka. Apakah kesudahan hubungan mereka berdua.

programme.title: Kad Cinta
programme.desc: TK mencintai Julia, seorang pelajar universiti di Istanbul. Pertemuan mereka di lapangan terbang Istanbul menimbulkan bibit-bibit cinta. Ingin menampung perbelanjaan kajian, TK pulang ke Malaysia dan bekerja sebagai penghantar surat. Ketika menghantar bungkusan, TK bertemu kembali dengan Julia. Sejak itu, Julia sering menerima kad misteri daripada seorang peminat. Berjayakah Julia membongkar persoalan siapakah yang sering menghantar kad misteri tersebut?

programme.title: Antara Gadis
programme.desc: Zarul, seorang yang sangat bekerja keras sanggup berniaga ketika sedang belajar kerana ingin menampung pengajiannya. Bapa kepada kekasihnya, Dato' Majid turut membantu perniagaannya. Kekasihnya, Nora yang menuntut di luar negara pulang selepas tamat pengajian namun menemui Zarul yang menghadapi kesukaran dalam pembelajaran dan percintaan.

programme.title: Sate
programme.desc: Milah ialah seorang peniaga sate dan kedai satenya terletak di hadapan bengkel kepunyaan Kadir yang suka melakukan eksperimen aneh. Kadir ingin menyertai Anugerah Saintis untuk memenangi hadiah utama dan sekaligus menyenangkan hidup Milah. Pelbagai rintangan terpaksa dia lalui untuk mencipta mesin miliknya dan akhirnya Kadir berjaya menyiapkan mesin tersebut dan menyertai pertandingan itu.

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: Debu Debu Kasih
programme.desc: Suzana baru pulang dari Amerika dengan membawa ijazah dalam bidang muzik. Dia mengikut kawannya Linda untuk bercuti di Terengganu. Di Terengganu, Suzana berkenalan dengan Hassan – seorang pemuda yang suka menghabiskan masa dengan memerhatikan orang di jeti sambil bermain gitar. Suzana akhirnya membantu Hassan sehingga menjadi seorang penyanyi yang berjaya dan telah jatuh cinta dengan Hassan. Namun Suzana telah dikejutkan dengan perubahan sikap Hassan secara tiba-tiba.

Amelia enggan menurut kehendak ibunya kerana Jefri seorang kaki perempuan. Bapa Amelia juga menentang keputusan itu dan bertemu Fandy untuk menceritakan segala yang berlaku. Fandy berasa bersalah kerana menganggap dirinya punca keluarga Amelia berantakan. Fandy mengambil keputusan untuk membawa diri ke luar negara dan hal ini telah menyebabkan Amelia terpaksa mengahwini Jefri. Selepas berkahwin, Amelia dijangkiti HIV daripada suaminya. Apabila Fandy mengetahui keadaan sebenar, dia ingin menebus segala kesalahannya terhadap Amelia.

programme.title: Rozana Cinta 87
programme.desc: Kuala Lumpur menjadi saksi cinta antara Rozana, anak orang berpengaruh dengan seorang pelukis di Pasar Seni yang bernama Din. Rozana mengikuti kelas tarian dan bertemu dengan Nomi. Tanpa disedari, Nomi turut menaruh perasaan terhadap Rozana.

programme.title: Kad Cinta
programme.desc: TK mencintai Julia, seorang pelajar universiti di Istanbul. Pertemuan mereka di lapangan terbang Istanbul menimbulkan bibit-bibit cinta. Ingin menampung perbelanjaan kajian, TK pulang ke Malaysia dan bekerja sebagai penghantar surat. Ketika menghantar bungkusan, TK bertemu kembali dengan Julia. Sejak itu, Julia sering menerima kad misteri daripada seorang peminat. Berjayakah Julia membongkar persoalan siapakah yang sering menghantar kad misteri tersebut?

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: Debu Debu Kasih
programme.desc: Suzana baru pulang dari Amerika dengan membawa ijazah dalam bidang muzik. Dia mengikut kawannya Linda untuk bercuti di Terengganu. Di Terengganu, Suzana berkenalan dengan Hassan – seorang pemuda yang suka menghabiskan masa dengan memerhatikan orang di jeti sambil bermain gitar. Suzana akhirnya membantu Hassan sehingga menjadi seorang penyanyi yang berjaya dan telah jatuh cinta dengan Hassan. Namun Suzana telah dikejutkan dengan perubahan sikap Hassan secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: KLU
programme.desc: Maria, pelajar universiti di luar negara pulang ke tanahair kerana ayahnya yang sakit menyambung semula pelajarannya secara tempatan. Ayah Maria, Datuk Nordin yang sakit telah pun sembuh dan merupakan seorang yang sangat kaya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Tuan Hudson yang semakin muflis mengatur langkah untuk memastikan anaknya, Bob mendekatkan dirinya dengan Maria demi harta.

programme.title: Sate
programme.desc: Milah ialah seorang peniaga sate dan kedai satenya terletak di hadapan bengkel kepunyaan Kadir yang suka melakukan eksperimen aneh. Kadir ingin menyertai Anugerah Saintis untuk memenangi hadiah utama dan sekaligus menyenangkan hidup Milah. Pelbagai rintangan terpaksa dia lalui untuk mencipta mesin miliknya dan akhirnya Kadir berjaya menyiapkan mesin tersebut dan menyertai pertandingan itu.

programme.title: Putera
programme.desc: Seorang putera raja bernama Hussein menemui cinta bersama seorang gadis biasa. Namun dia dijodohkan bersama Puteri Balqis. Mereka ke Paris namun Hussein terlihat Balqis bermesraan bersama lelaki lain. Bapa Hussein memeberinya masa selama 30 hari untuk mencari calon isteri jika tidak mahu berkahwin dengan Puteri Balqis. Pelbagai halangan terpaksa mereka tempuhi demi mengecapi cinta.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep955956
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! programme.desc: Different in age, generation, and hosting style, these three hosts not only can sing, act, dance, and imitate, but are also skilled in cross-talk! With this unique combination, we hope to attract viewers of all ages and spark great entertainment.

programme.title: Stories In Taiwan (T) Ep1034
programme.desc: In a playful and relaxed style, the host went deep into the corners of various towns and villages in Taiwan, looking for the uniqueness, introduced the special local customs and traditions.

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the world’s best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the world’s top detective got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun…

programme.title: My School Mate, The Barbarian
programme.desc: Edward attends a new school which has a reputation for fighting. Student leader Stone, befriends Edward, but their friendship is tested when a local triad leader discovers that Edward comes from a wealthy family.

programme.title: Finding Mr. Right
programme.desc: A woman from Beijing, pregnant with the child of her rich married boyfriend, flies to Seattle in order to deliver the baby. She meets a Chinese immigrant man working as a driver there, and as she starts to learn more about him, her life begins to change.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kong’s legendary detective?

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: Kung Fu Monster
programme.desc: In the Ming Dynasty, the Bruneian Empire offers a monster as a gift to the nation. Imperial guard Ocean is tasked to train it, but realizing it is a kind creature by nature, he releases it secretly so that it will not become a killing beast. His action prompts a frenzy hunt for the monster when the palace puts a hefty bounty for its return…

programme.title: Dad, I'm Sorry
programme.desc: Ba Sang lives in a poor district in Saigon and his son Woan is a Youtuber earning considerable income. Woan wants his father to enjoy retirement, so he is mad at him for being a meddler and making unnecessary sacrifices. This has created conflicts between the two generations and leads to a crisis in the father and son relationship.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his family’s expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family’s reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Long’s daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity…

programme.title: My Love
programme.desc: Adapted from a Korean movie, this is the love story of school swimmer Zhou Xiao Qi and a transfer student You Yong Ci. Zhou falls in love with You at first sight in high school but You leaves suddenly one day without saying goodbye. As fate brings them back together years later, can they get the spark back in their relationship?

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the police’s only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: A Wedding Invitation
programme.desc: A boy’s marriage proposal was rejected by the girl and the lovers separated. Nonetheless, they agree on a break-up contract stating that if both are single in five years they will get married. Can they finally be together?

programme.title: Paradox
programme.desc: Hong Kong Police officer Li travels to Thailand to search for his daughter when she disappears mysteriously. He teams up with a local detective to investigate and they chance upon a black market organ smuggling ring which could throw light on his daughter’s whereabouts...

programme.title: Romantic Dream
programme.desc: Dino meets his dream girl Mandy and falls in love with her at first sight. However, she disappears suddenly and he only sees her again after nine years, when she is already married. To overcome the pain of losing his love, Dino finds a guru with supernatural power to make him meet Mandy in his dream.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Project Gutenberg
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police hunts for a counterfeiting gang led by a mastermind known as Painter. The gang is so skillful that it's almost impossible to distinguish between its counterfeit currency and real money. In an effort to find Painter's real identity, the Police recruits artist Lee Man to assist in solving the case.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: MMA Diva
programme.desc: Xin Lan takes over her father’s MMA club which is heavily in debt due to poor business. After He Hua defeated Xin Lan, she replaces her to become the new top MMA Diva and challenges Xin Lan’s MMA club to a duel. As Xin Lan is injured, she seeks help from a retried MMA superstar to fight the battle on her behalf to reclaim the club’s and her honour.

programme.title: Love on a Diet
programme.desc: Mini's broken heart leads her to pack on the pounds. She meets an obese man named Fatso who helps her get back on track and shed the pounds. After dropping the unwanted heft, Mini rekindles her relationship with her first love, but is this the happy ending that she wants?

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Push and Shove
programme.desc: A puppy gets gravely injured while defending them from the neighbor's large and aggressive Tibetan Mastiff. The arrogant owner of the Tibetan Mastiff, however, refuses to take responsibility, and the police aren't of much help since no people were hurt. When push comes to shove, the puppy’s owner vows to fight for justice for his dog.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kong’s legendary detective?

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Chang’s first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunt’s puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: The Thundering Sword
programme.desc: Two disciples, Yu and Zheng, are sent by their master to track down the invincible weapon “Thundering Sword” to prevent villains from getting it. Yu encounters the daughter of a ruthless clan, Chiao, who is on her way to seek for the sword. They quickly fall for each other, but when Chiao accidentally injures Zheng, things become complicated.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: The Dancing Millionaires is of the most enjoyable musicals to grace the Hong Kong screens, starring husband & wife team Peter Chen Ho and Betty Loh Ti presenting some extraordinary performances.

programme.title: Pursuit
programme.desc: This movie tells the tale of Lin Chong, the Sung Dynasty’s Chief Army Instructor who is framed by a corrupt official and has to embark on an exile fraught with danger. Helped by a monk, Lin Chong is finally able to take revenge.

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Perils Of The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: The titanic team of Director Chu Yuan and Novelist Ku Lung chose to give their hero (Ti Lung) a whole new cliffhanger-fraught adventure featuring a mysterious swordsman, a sensual swordswoman, an imperial assassin, a ghost mansion, a booby-trapped tunnel, as well as double crosses and secret missions.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a General’s daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Dragon Swamp
programme.desc: Fan is cheated by her lover Tong to steal her master’s Jade Dragon Sword. She is jailed in the Dragon Swamp as punishment and gave birth to a pair of twins - her daughter is raised by her master, while her son is taken by Tong. Twenty years later, the sword is stolen again and Fan’s daughter goes seeking for it, meeting Fan’s friend along the way.

programme.title: Sex, Love and Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: Ten Tigers of Kwang Tung
programme.desc: The Ten Tigers of Kwang Tung is a group of anti-Ching martial artists who have killed a Ching official. Years later, when five disciples and descendants of Ten Tigers meet one night, one of them is killed by the son of the late Ching official who returns with a vengeance. They must fight against him to protect the Ten Tigers clan…

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Wang Yu plays Kwei Wu, who stumbles onto a kidnapping with his wife Kan Lien-chu (Chin Ping) at the Red Lotus Temple. Kan sends Kwei to go for reinforcements while she stays to fight the kidnappers, but she is captured and imprisoned in an iron cage. As Kwei returns with reinforcements, he must also race to the temple to save his wife.

programme.title: Clan of Amazons
programme.desc: The martial arts world is plunged into terror when a mysterious figure known as the 'Embroidery Bandit' starts to attack convoys of precious materials. Seemingly unstoppable, the frightened clans decide to call on the expertise of Lu Xiao Feng, an inquisitive fighter and detective to capture the culprit.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, she’s soon framed for her husband’s murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense…

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to trap Wong’s disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong thus to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: The story follows Monk Tang San Zang’s (Ho Fan) journey to the West in search of the Buddhist Sutra. On the way, he encounters and takes as disciples, Monkey (Yueh Hua), Pigsy (Peng Peng) and Sha Wu Jing (Tien Shun).

programme.title: The Battle Wizard
programme.desc: Dali Prince Tuan Yu knows nothing about martial arts, but leaves the palace for the martial arts world. He meets a snake sorceress and his mysterious half-sister. Through various misadventures, Tuan Yu gains invincible power by sucking the cobra’s blood and swallowing the magic toad, eventually defeating his father’s old rival.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Mui’s embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love…

programme.title: The Golden Buddha
programme.desc: A map indicating the location of the Chan’s family heirloom is hidden in three Golden Buddha statues. Paul, an insurance agent, finds one statue by chance and Chan’s daughter has another one. This makes them targets of treasure-hunting criminals and they have to team up to defeat them before unveiling the hidden secrets.

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: The Protectors
programme.desc: Ling Hsiao and Kuan Wang Lung are two guard chiefs working for an old convoy master. Lung is secretly in love with Fang Yen, the master’s granddaughter but Yen is attracted to Ling Hsiao instead. In order to win her back, Lung sets up a trap to steal the convoy and frames Ling Hsiao for it.

programme.title: Let's Fall In Love
programme.desc: Da Yung, the son of a rich entrepreneur, meets Lian Lian, the niece of a kindergarten principal by chance. They get into a misunderstanding at the first meeting, causing Da Yung to lose his wallet. Further misunderstanding occurs when he tries to use her to act as his fiancé, in order to drive away two women whom he does not like…

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friend’s grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: Iron Bodyguard
programme.desc: Wang Wu, the head of a security firm Iron Bodyguard, meets a scholar who is a member of the Reformists, a group of scholars pressing for social reform in China at the end of the Qing dynasty. The Emperor actually supports such reforms but not the Empress Dowager. She orders the Reformists to be arrested and Wang Wu gets drawn into the politics.

programme.title: Rolls, Rolls, I Love You
programme.desc: Three young men offend a billionaire and are drawn into a high stakes bet. If they win, they get to keep the billionaire’s Rolls Royce. Otherwise, they will need to pay the rich man fifty thousand dollars! Will the underdogs win the bet?

programme.title: Finger of Doom
programme.desc: The protagonists are ex-swordmasters who now find joy in making umbrellas. They track down the evil Madame Kung Sun and her poisonous “Finger of Doom”, a unique supernatural power which allows her to transform normal, everyday people into horrifying zombies, and this is just the start of their mythical adventure against this zombie maker!

programme.title: The Duel of the Century
programme.desc: In the mid-1980's Chu Yuan became internationally famous for starring as the nasty villain in Jackie Chan's groundbreaking worldwide hit, POLICE STORY. But for more than twenty-five years, he was famous as one of Hong Kong’s most respected directors of "Martial-art World" epics — often conceived by his remarkable collaborator, novelist Ku Lung. This was one of their last together for the Shaw Brothers Studio, but it's another revenge and mystery-tinged winner. Liu Yung and Sun Chien (the Korean kicking THE FIVE VENOM from Chang Cheh's internationally popular series) team to investigate the martial-art murders of a supposedly mortally wounded swordsman, only to find deception, double-dealings, imposters, and one deadly duel after another. No less than three choreographers are on hand to handle the multitude of martial arts, making this one of Chu Yuan's most involving and exciting efforts ever.

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui and Ha are stuck in their unhappy marriages and are attracted to each other when they meet at a party. In one of their beach strolls, Ha picks up a purple shell and gives it to Hui as a memento. When Hui’s husband finds out about them, he hurts Hui and cause her to become seriously ill, while also blackmails Ha. How will this love story end?

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor (The Chinese Boxer) and action choreographer (Jackie Chan's Drunken Master), the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan (Once Upon A Time In China) and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li (Snake In The Eagle's Shadow) everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: Godfather of Canton
programme.desc: Commissioner Liu Ta-hua (Tsao Ta-hua) is arrested by special envoy Cheng Chih-cheng (Wang Jung) for corruption. Coolie Lin Szu-hai (Gordon Liu Chia-hui), who has unintentionally helped Cheng, is given a small post under Lo. Lin is smart and soon learns how to get dockside bribes. Later, he gets a regular spin-off from Adjutant Chang…

programme.title: The House of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxer
programme.desc: Skilled shadow Tai Chi boxer Ku Ting hides his skills by working as a construction worker. However, when the thugs assaulted his girlfriend, Ku Ting has no choice but to use his kung fu to show his enemies what it takes to keep justice in line.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends’ help.

programme.title: Death Duel
programme.desc: Third Master is a renowned swordsman in the martial arts world, but the constant challenges by other swordsmen compel him to fake his death and pursue a secluded life. This does not prevent others from seeking him out to challenge him however, and he is forced to return to fight his way till the end.

programme.title: UFC 284: Makhachev vs. Volkanovski
programme.desc: Prelims - When the Octagon returns to Australia on February 12, a SuperFight will be on tap for the UFC 284 mainevent at RAC Arena in Perth, as newly-crowned lightweight champion Islam Makhachev defends his title for the first time against the undisputed eatherweight champion, Australia’s own Alexander Volkanovski. Looking to join the exclusive list of double-champs in UFC history, Volkanovski enters his first fight on home soil since 2018 on the heels of a dominant 145-pound reign that includes four successful title defenses over the likes of Max Holloway, Brian Ortega and Chan Sung Jung. But in February, he will be put to the test by Dagestan’s Makhachev, a dominant presence in his own right who extended his current winning streak to 11 in October when he submitted Charles Oliveira in the second round to win the 155-pound championship he will defend against Alexander “The Great”. Plus, the interim featherweight title will be on the line in the co-main event when top contenders Yair Rodriguez and Josh Emmett collide in what promises to an explosive five-round championship bout, and former world champion Robert Whittaker faces Paulo Cos

programme.title: UFC 284: Makhachev vs. Volkanovski
programme.desc: Prelims - When the Octagon returns to Australia on February 12, a SuperFight will be on tap for the UFC 284 mainevent at RAC Arena in Perth, as newly-crowned lightweight champion Islam Makhachev defends his title for the first time against the undisputed eatherweight champion, Australia’s own Alexander Volkanovski. Looking to join the exclusive list of double-champs in UFC history, Volkanovski enters his first fight on home soil since 2018 on the heels of a dominant 145-pound reign that includes four successful title defenses over the likes of Max Holloway, Brian Ortega and Chan Sung Jung. But in February, he will be put to the test by Dagestan’s Makhachev, a dominant presence in his own right who extended his current winning streak to 11 in October when he submitted Charles Oliveira in the second round to win the 155-pound championship he will defend against Alexander “The Great”. Plus, the interim featherweight title will be on the line in the co-main event when top contenders Yair Rodriguez and Josh Emmett collide in what promises to an explosive five-round championship bout, and former world champion Robert Whittaker faces Paulo Cos
